{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_14","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"rg -n '\\\"jni\\\"|JNI' metadata | head -n 200\"","aggregated_output":"metadata/org.jline/jline-native/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"JLine Native Library packages JNI bindings and platform-specific native binaries used by JLine to access low-level terminal functionality. It provides Java APIs and native resources for POSIX and Windows console operations, including metadata needed when the library is used in GraalVM Native Image builds.\",\nmetadata/org.jline/jline-terminal-jni/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"JLine JNI Terminal provides the JLine terminal provider implementation that uses JLine's JNI native library for low-level terminal and pseudoterminal access. It plugs into the JLine terminal API to support native console operations across supported platforms without relying on JNA or external process execution.\",\nmetadata/org.jline/jline-terminal-jni/index.json:43:    \"description\" : \"JLine JNI Terminal provides the JLine terminal provider implementation that uses JLine's JNI native library for low-level terminal and pseudoterminal access. It plugs into the JLine terminal API to support native console operations across supported platforms without relying on JNA or external process execution.\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:7:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4JNICompressor\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:18:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4HCJNICompressor\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:37:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4JNIFastDecompressor\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:48:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4JNISafeDecompressor\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:163:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.xxhash.XXHash32JNI\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:174:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.xxhash.StreamingXXHash32JNI$Factory\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:185:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.xxhash.XXHash64JNI\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/1.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:196:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.xxhash.StreamingXXHash64JNI$Factory\",\nmetadata/org.lz4/lz4-java/index.json:10:    \"description\": \"lz4-java provides Java ports and bindings for the LZ4 compression algorithm and the xxHash hashing algorithm. It offers JNI, pure Java, and Unsafe-based implementations for fast compression, decompression, and hashing.\",\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-transport-native-unix-common/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Netty Transport Native Unix Common provides shared JNI-backed Unix utility classes and native support used by Netty's Unix-based transport modules. It supplies common Unix socket address, file descriptor, and native library plumbing that higher-level Netty transports build on for asynchronous network clients and servers.\",\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-transport-native-unix-common/index.json:45:    \"description\" : \"Netty Transport Native Unix Common provides shared JNI-backed Unix utility classes and native support used by Netty's Unix-based transport modules. It supplies common Unix socket address, file descriptor, and native library plumbing that higher-level Netty transports build on for asynchronous network clients and servers.\",\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-transport-native-epoll/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Netty Transport Native Epoll provides Linux epoll-based native transport support for Netty. It gives Netty applications high-performance event loops, channels, and JNI-backed native socket features on Linux.\",\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-transport-native-kqueue/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Netty Transport Native KQueue provides Netty's native kqueue-based transport implementation for macOS, FreeBSD, and OpenBSD. It packages JNI/native code and Java channel and event-loop classes so Netty applications can use the operating system's kqueue event notification API for high-performance asynchronous networking.\",\nmetadata/org.fusesource.hawtjni/hawtjni-runtime/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"HawtJNI Runtime provides the annotations and helper API that projects using HawtJNI compile against. It includes the runtime classes used to describe JNI bindings and load bundled native libraries from Java.\",\nmetadata/com.github.luben/zstd-jni/index.json:8:    \"description\" : \"zstd-jni provides Java and JVM JNI bindings for the Zstandard compression library, including APIs for compressing and decompressing byte arrays. It also includes stream-based InputStream and OutputStream implementations that transparently read and write Zstandard-compressed data.\",\nmetadata/com.github.luben/zstd-jni/index.json:23:    \"description\" : \"zstd-jni provides JNI bindings for the Zstandard compression library to Java and other JVM languages. It exposes byte-array and stream-based APIs for compressing and decompressing data using the bundled native implementation.\",\nmetadata/com.github.luben/zstd-jni/index.json:51:    \"description\" : \"zstd-jni provides JNI bindings for the Zstandard compression library to Java, Android, and other JVM languages. It offers byte-array and stream-based APIs for compressing and decompressing data using bundled native binaries.\",\nmetadata/schemas/reachability-metadata-schema-v1.2.0.json:103:            \"title\": \"Allow objects of this class to be instantiated with a call to jdk.internal.misc.Unsafe#allocateInstance or JNI's AllocObject\",\nmetadata/schemas/reachability-metadata-schema-v1.2.0.json:113:            \"title\": \"Register the type, including all registered fields and methods, for runtime JNI access\",\nmetadata/net.java.dev.jna/jna/index.json:12:    \"description\": \"JNA provides Java programs with easy access to native shared libraries without requiring JNI code. It lets Java code call native functions and map native data structures through Java interfaces and classes.\",\nmetadata/net.java.dev.jna/jna/5.8.0/reachability-metadata.json:98:      \"type\": \"com.sun.jna.JNIEnv\",\nmetadata/org.rocksdb/rocksdbjni/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"RocksDB JNI provides Java bindings for RocksDB, an embeddable persistent key-value store optimized for fast storage. The rocksdbjni artifact packages the native RocksDB libraries for supported platforms so Java applications can use RocksDB without building native binaries separately.\",\nmetadata/org.rocksdb/rocksdbjni/index.json:33:    \"description\" : \"RocksDB JNI provides Java bindings for RocksDB, an embeddable persistent key-value store optimized for fast storage on flash and RAM. The rocksdbjni artifact packages the native RocksDB libraries for supported platforms so Java applications can use RocksDB without building them separately.\",\nmetadata/org.rocksdb/rocksdbjni/index.json:47:    \"description\" : \"RocksDB JNI provides Java bindings for RocksDB, an embeddable persistent key-value store optimized for fast storage on flash and RAM. The rocksdbjni artifact packages the native RocksDB libraries for supported platforms so Java applications can use RocksDB without building them separately.\",\nmetadata/at.yawk.lz4/lz4-java/1.10.4/reachability-metadata.json:7:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4JNICompressor\",\nmetadata/at.yawk.lz4/lz4-java/1.10.4/reachability-metadata.json:18:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4HCJNICompressor\",\nmetadata/at.yawk.lz4/lz4-java/1.10.4/reachability-metadata.json:37:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4JNIFastDecompressor\",\nmetadata/at.yawk.lz4/lz4-java/1.10.4/reachability-metadata.json:48:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.lz4.LZ4JNISafeDecompressor\",\nmetadata/at.yawk.lz4/lz4-java/1.10.4/reachability-metadata.json:152:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.xxhash.XXHash32JNI\",\nmetadata/at.yawk.lz4/lz4-java/1.10.4/reachability-metadata.json:163:      \"type\": \"net.jpountz.xxhash.St